TI Optimal Recall from Bounded Metaplastic Synapses: Predicting Functional
   Adaptations in Hippocampal Area CA3
SO PLOS COMPUTATIONAL BIOLOGY
LA English
DT Article
ID PRESYNAPTIC NEURONAL EXCITABILITY; DEPENDENT SYNAPTIC PLASTICITY;
   NEURAL-NETWORKS; GAMMA-OSCILLATIONS; PYRAMIDAL CELLS; INTRINSIC
   EXCITABILITY; INFORMATION-STORAGE; ASSOCIATIVE MEMORY; RAT HIPPOCAMPUS;
